l for the S-N BDEs. The abovementioned DFT methods\nare capable of capturing the change in electronic structure and properties of\nthe -SNO fragment, when the CH$_3$SNO molecule is exposed to the influence of\nphysiologically feasible external electric field $F_Z$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Apr 2017 08:15:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 9 May 2017 21:10:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-13"}
